      "span_text": "To make use of this localized feature, existing algorithms such as Dynamic Brushfire and its subsequent variants aim to speed up the reconstruction by launching a wavefront from the source of the state changes to incrementally repair the distance values, rather than reconstructing the whole DM from scratch."
